BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 738 Tm (This implementation does not reproduce the paper line by line. Instead, it adapts the) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 723 Tm (paper's core reinforcement learning ideas into a cleaner engineering-focused system:) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 699.0 Tm (- one learning agent instead of two competing learners) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 684.0 Tm (- a rule-based ghost instead of a learned adversary) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 669.0 Tm (- an image-like grid state for deep learning) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 654.0 Tm (- curriculum learning and replay-based training) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 639.0 Tm (- practical reward shaping for survival and pellet completion) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 615.0 Tm (The resulting system is closer to a robust applied RL prototype than a pure reproduction of) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 600.0 Tm (the research benchmark.) Tj ET
