BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 444.0 Tm (- Channel 4: ghost timing cue) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 420.0 Tm (The timing cue indicates whether the ghost is about to move, allowing the network to reason) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 405.0 Tm (not only about where danger is, but also when danger is likely to change.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 381.0 Tm (This representation gives the agent explicit awareness of:) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 357.0 Tm (- geometry) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 342.0 Tm (- food locations) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 327.0 Tm (- its own position) Tj ET
