BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 297.0 Tm (- movement rhythm of the ghost) Tj ET
BT /F2 14 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 273.0 Tm (6. Reward System) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 243.0 Tm (The reward function was tuned to reflect the desired gameplay behavior while remaining) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 228.0 Tm (stable enough for DQN training.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 204.0 Tm (The final main rewards are:) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 180.0 Tm (- Empty cell: -0.1) Tj ET
