BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 738 Tm (- tiny anti-oscillation penalties for standing still, immediate backtracking, and) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 723 Tm (  revisiting recent cells) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 708 Tm (- a small bonus for moving closer to the nearest pellet) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 684.0 Tm (The purpose of these shaping terms is not to replace the main objective, but to help the) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 669.0 Tm (network discover policies that are both productive and stable.) Tj ET
BT /F2 14 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 645.0 Tm (7. Neural Network Architecture) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 615.0 Tm (### 7.1 Model Type) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 591.0 Tm (The agent uses a convolutional Deep Q-Network implemented in PyTorch.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 567.0 Tm (### 7.2 Feature Extractor) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 543.0 Tm (The state tensor is passed through stacked convolutional layers:) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 519.0 Tm (- Conv2d\(5 -> 8\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 504.0 Tm (- Conv2d\(8 -> 16\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 489.0 Tm (- Conv2d\(16 -> 32\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 465.0 Tm (Each convolution is followed by a ReLU activation. These layers allow the model to detect) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 450.0 Tm (local spatial patterns such as:) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 426.0 Tm (- corridors) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 411.0 Tm (- dead ends) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 396.0 Tm (- pellet clusters) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 381.0 Tm (- relative ghost danger) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 366.0 Tm (- safe escape routes) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 342.0 Tm (### 7.3 Dueling Architecture) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 318.0 Tm (The current implementation uses a dueling DQN structure. After convolutional features are) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 303.0 Tm (flattened, the network splits into:) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 279.0 Tm (- a value stream V\(s\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 264.0 Tm (- an advantage stream A\(s, a\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 240.0 Tm (The final Q-value is computed as:) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 216.0 Tm (Q\(s, a\) = V\(s\) + A\(s, a\) - mean\(A\(s, a\)\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 192.0 Tm (This helps the model learn which states are generally good or bad independently of the) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 177.0 Tm (immediate action ranking, which can improve stability in tasks with many similar actions.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 153.0 Tm (### 7.4 Action Selection) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 129.0 Tm (Action selection uses epsilon-greedy exploration:) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 105.0 Tm (- with probability epsilon, choose a random legal action) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 90.0 Tm (- otherwise, choose the legal action with highest Q-value) Tj ET
endstream
