BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 540.0 Tm (The current system still has important limitations:) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 516.0 Tm (- one ghost instead of multiple ghosts) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 501.0 Tm (- deterministic ghost policy rather than stochastic behavior) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 486.0 Tm (- single fixed maze layout) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 471.0 Tm (- no transfer learning across maps) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 456.0 Tm (- DQN limitations in very sparse or long-horizon settings) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 432.0 Tm (These limitations do not invalidate the project, but they define its scope. This is a) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 417.0 Tm (focused RL system, not a full clone of commercial Pac-Man.) Tj ET
