BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 339.0 Tm (- periodic evaluation episodes with fixed settings and epsilon = 0) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 324.0 Tm (- checkpointing based on evaluation wins rather than training reward) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 309.0 Tm (- multiple maze layouts for better generalization) Tj ET
