BT /F2 14 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 210.0 Tm (16. Conclusion) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 180.0 Tm (PacManDRL is a strong end-to-end reinforcement learning project that combines environment) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 165.0 Tm (engineering, neural network design, curriculum learning, and practical debugging into a) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 150.0 Tm (cohesive system. It goes beyond a toy example because the agent learns non-trivial spatial) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 135.0 Tm (and temporal behavior: it collects pellets, avoids a pursuing ghost, adapts to maze) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 120.0 Tm (structure, and shows evidence of meaningful policy learning.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 96.0 Tm (The final system is especially valuable because it demonstrates the full workflow of applied) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 1 0 0 1 54 81.0 Tm (reinforcement learning:) Tj ET
